# File organization

- Scripts: repo `bin/`.
- Docs: repo `doc/` — one topic per file.
- App code: `web/src/` — `actions/`, `app/`, `components/`, `lib/`, `hooks/`, `utils/`.
- Domain modules in `lib/{domain}/` when 2+ related files; feature orchestration in `actions/` (see `actions-vs-lib.mdc`).
